profile:
At Mega Roofing & Exteriors Inc. we offer a wide range of high-quality exterior services throughout southern Alberta, specializing in all roofing applications, exterior cladding (including vinyl and cement board) soffit/fascia & eavestroughs both 5" & 6". We also offer 24 hour emergency repair response line for any of our services.
Our company's core values are Honesty & Integrity, and we take extreme pride in our workmanship & exceptional customer service. We strive to go above and beyond, to ensure every client's satisfaction, whether it is an eavestrough cleaning, small repair service or a complete exterior renovation (roof, siding, all soft metals). 
We have financing facilities available (OAC).

profile:
Roof Right Solutions is a professional, trustworthy, family owned company that specializes into fibreglass asphalt shingles, eco-friendly rubber roofs and eavestrough replacement in around the Calgary area. At Roof Right Solutions, we have built dedicated teams of professionals who pride themselves in offering courteous services. We always ensure of delivering the highest quality of roofing/soft metal products - from low budgets to higher budgets, we offer the best product options including different grades of laminated asphalt fiberglass shingles and eco-friendly Euroshield rubber products.

Roof Right Solutions is licensed,insured and is covered with WCB. We are also accredited on BBB. Roof Right Solutions is a Certified Malarkey Contractor and obtained the HAAG Certification to assess hail damages.

profile:
Top Roof & Exteriors inc. is a Calgary based company established in 2012 with representatives that have been in the industry for as long as 40+ years! Top Roof & Exteriors provides unrivaled and exceptional roofing services in and around the southern Alberta area. Our highly experienced roofing team specializes in roof replacements and repairs for commercial, industrial and residential properties.

Integrity, professionalism and reliability are always our top priorities and our projects always meet or exceed Alberta Building Codes. We are fully insured to cover: Hot tar, and hot work, roofing and exteriors for both commercial and residential projects. We are also qualified and certified installers for all types of roofing systems and exterior work that we offer like; Torch on (SBS), EPDM, TPO, Spray on coating, Shingles, Cedar, Rubber, Metal, Siding, Eavestrough, Facia, Soffit, Railing and Painting. We really go the extra mile to ensure that our jobs are safe sites and we are proud to be SECOR Certified.  Our workmanship is outstanding and we offer a 10 year workmanship warranty on all of our work.

Before undergoing any work, we will carefully inspect the premises, discuss available options, estimate costs and provide you with solutions that match your needs and budget. Top Roof takes great pride in offering personalized service, which means our clients get to choose the plan that is best suited for their home/business. As a premier company specializing in residential and commercial roofing services, we are dedicated to providing customer service that is second to none. 

Whether you have a new construction project or need to replace an old or damaged roof, we should be your go-to roofing repair and replacement service.
